# Documentation Assets

This directory is reserved for documentation assets such as:
- Architecture diagrams
- Screenshots
- Demo GIFs
- Flow charts

## Placeholder Files

When adding demo assets, use descriptive names like:
- `architecture-diagram.png`
- `home-page-screenshot.png`
- `prediction-flow.gif`
- `health-dashboard.png`

## Referencing in README

Assets can be referenced in markdown files using relative paths:
```markdown
![Architecture Diagram](./docs/assets/architecture-diagram.png)
```
